        <div class="audience-head"><span class="audience-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/></svg></span><h3>For players</h3></div>
        <ul class="audience-list">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Fairer, closer games every time you play</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Less standing around - the courts keep moving</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> A rating that reflects how you actually play</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="audience-card">
        <div class="audience-head"><span class="audience-ico"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="4" width="14" height="17" rx="2"/><path d="M9 4h6v3H9z"/><path d="M8.5 13l2 2 4-4"/></svg></span><h3>For organisers</h3></div>
        <ul class="audience-list">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Your evening back - the picking and admin run themselves</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Fewer "that's not fair" conversations</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Players who enjoy it and keep coming back</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SOCIAL PROOF -->
<section class="bg-soft">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">33,000+</div><div class="lbl">games played</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">1,100+</div><div class="lbl">club sessions run</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num">2,000+</div><div class="lbl">players rated</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="quote">
      <p>&ldquo;I was finding that everyone turned to me to get games on, taking into account all the things that your software did - who had been benched for a while, who pairs up well and who has an equal amount of games. I honestly cannot sing your praises enough, because it did almost everything we needed it to.&rdquo;</p>
      <div class="who">- South Gippsland Badminton Association, Melbourne</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FINAL CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Run your club on ePegboard, free</h2>
    <p>No subscription. No card details. Just smarter club nights.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" style="background:#fff" href="https://play.epegboard.com/signup" target="_blank">Sign up at play.epegboard.com</a>
